(c) 2006, Jon Phillips <jon AT rejon DOT org>
(c) 2010, Khaled Hosny <khaledhosnt AT eglug DOT org>

A simple font viewer


BUILDING
========

Requires Gtk+ 2.16+, Cairo, Pango, Freetype2.

To build:

    make


To run:
 
    ./fontview /path/to/a/typeface
 

To clean:

    make clean

 
See COPYING for license information.
